{"name": "pool-resources", "metadata": {"name": "pool-resources", "version": "0.3.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://gitlab.com/mihaicristianpirvu/pool-resources", "license": "WTFPL", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["torch", "pytorch_lightning"], "summary": "Pool Resources", "upload_time": 1711205027}, "documentation": ["# Pool Resources\n\n## Description\nLibrary to generalize `multiprocessing.Pool(n: int)` to handle generic resources.\n\nFirst class support for torch devices as a generic resource.\n\n## Example for n torch GPUs and k torch Modules\n\n```\nfrom pool_resources import PoolResources\nfrom pool_resources.resources import TorchResource\n\nclass Model(nn.Module):\n    def __init__(self, input_shape, output_shape):\n        super().__init__()\n        self.fc = nn.Linear(input_shape, output_shape)\n\n    def forward(self, x):\n        return self.fc(x)\n\ndef forward_fn(item):\n    model, data = item\n    return model.forward(data)\n\nmodules = [Model(input_shape=20, output_shape=30) for _ in range(k)]\ndata = tr.randn(k, B, 20)\nseq = zip(modules, data)\n\nresources = [TorchResource(f\"cuda:{i}\") for i in range(n)]\n\nres_sequential = list(map(forward_fn, seq))\nres_parallel = PoolResources(resources).map(forward_fn, seq)\n\n\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "setup", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "setup.get_reqs", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "requirements", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "setup.name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.description", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.url", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.loc", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.long_description", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.req_file", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.requirements", "ty